{"tid":269344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[六晚嘉年華化] 快樂抗爭嘉年華　打鼓唱歌 high翻天 OL：咁嘅香港先似樣","createTime":"2017-06-03T16:32:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T16:46:51.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0fd85a1e5cf5ed5e14fe8b3e5b0e1c7252292f35","tid":269344,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:32:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20100109/13608947\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20100109%2F13608947&d=ul1OOknNQ2%2BL8WNHQg6mcp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=e232eb6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20100109%2F13608947&h=9c80b41c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20100109/13608947</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20100109/large/09la2p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20100109%2Flarge%2F09la2p1.jpg&h=93a0b3f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20100109/large/A04_01_d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20100109%2Flarge%2FA04_01_d.gif&h=5f555858&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】紅紅藍藍的帳篷如花開遍名廈林立的中環，香港的商業中心昨天舉辦嘉年華；已經快要在這個城巿消失的舊日巿集、已經快要被「高速發展」所唾棄的社區經濟，在中環短暫復活一天。50後、60後、70後、80後，無分年齡先後，人人神態從容，展現對未來的盼望，對政府霸權拆村不再視而不顧，對不公義的小圈子選舉不再沉默。抗爭，要快樂，抗爭，要堅持到最後。黃昏下班的 OL走過，感慨說：「咁樣嘅香港先似番啲樣。」<br />\n記者：雷子樂、張嘉雯、張文傑、謝明明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20100109/large/A04_01_b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20100109%2Flarge%2FA04_01_b.gif&h=993a51df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱鬧的議事堂外，氣溫低見14℃，溫熱的「不遷不拆鹹湯丸」、清香的「暖入心大地能量番薯糖水」、飽肚的「功能組別一舊飯」，連繫每個抗爭的巿民。有人全身髹上綠油，有人穿上鮮色太空衣，地上放着菜園模型、欄杆貼滿「沒有資格代表香港人」的功能組別議員照片。婦女們、年輕人個個埋頭苦幹，示威者萬眾一心，成就香港首個抗爭嘉年華。<br />\n<br />\n下午4時，財委會會議開始，場外的嘉年華正式展開，已解散的 indie樂隊「永遠懷念塔可夫斯基」揭開序幕，你打鼓，我唱歌，現場氣氛極為高漲，猶如台灣選舉的造勢晚會。抗爭者不時大喊「鄭汝樺大話精！」、「狗賊狗官！」、「歪理！」。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20100109/large/A04_01_a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20100109%2Flarge%2FA04_01_a.gif&h=17b5563c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c4183cfc98cc74452cacdd2966f0c6d997de5b0","tid":269344,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:46:51.000Z","msg":"左膠"}]}